textBox.richText: Started off with Alli, Max, and Gunter, but Alli's toe was bugging her, so she bailed. Gunter and Max and I headed over to Vasquez to do some more bumps...after a couple runs, Max took a spill and was done. Worked our way over to Jane base where we met up with Alli, then Gunter and I did two more bump runs before calling it a day.
